<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1978-03-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1978-03-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="162" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d162">
                        <head>162. Note From President <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> to Multiple Recipients<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d162fn1">Source: Carter Library, Papers of <persName corresp="#p_MWF_1">Walter F. Mondale</persName>, Box 206, Middle
                                East/Panama (1/1/1978–1/20/1981). No classification marking. Sent to
                                    <persName corresp="#p_MWF_1">Mondale</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_VCR_1">Vance</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_BGS_1">Brown</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_JH_1">Jordan</persName>, and <persName corresp="#p_MF_2">Moore</persName>.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1978-03-27">March 27, 1978</date>
                            </dateline>
                            <salute>To <persName corresp="#p_HEF_1">Fritz</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_VCR_1">Cy</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_PHR_1">Harold</persName>, Ham, <persName corresp="#p_CF_1">Frank</persName>
                            </salute>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The most important effort to be made during the next few days is to
                            insure the passage of the Panama Treaty.</p>
                        <p>Work <hi rend="italic">hard</hi> on this &amp; coordinate your efforts.
                                <persName corresp="#p_HEF_1">Fritz</persName> will lead.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed><persName><hi rend="strong">J.C.</hi></persName></signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>